=The Double=
=Episode 18=

2
00:00:09,880 --> 00:00:10,720
Mr. Zhao.

3
00:00:11,200 --> 00:00:12,520
Long time no see.

4
00:00:18,160 --> 00:00:20,320
We understand how you feel,

5
00:00:20,320 --> 00:00:22,440
but now that Li Ziyu is dead,

6
00:00:22,440 --> 00:00:24,680
how will Qinghe Group pay the money

7
00:00:25,400 --> 00:00:26,520
it owes us?

8
00:00:27,720 --> 00:00:29,880
I will take on all the responsibility.

9
00:00:30,600 --> 00:00:31,960
Take on responsibility?

10
00:00:32,680 --> 00:00:34,400
How will you do that?

11
00:00:35,280 --> 00:00:36,480
Zhao Jize,

12
00:00:36,480 --> 00:00:38,720
