13
00:00:39,200 --> 00:00:41,120
What are you?

14
00:00:41,600 --> 00:00:43,800
You're just a dog of the Li family.

15
00:00:45,640 --> 00:00:46,480
Hey!

16
00:00:46,720 --> 00:00:47,840
Don't go too far.

17
00:00:48,040 --> 00:00:50,280
Even a dog will jump over the wall
when it's desperate.

18
00:00:50,760 --> 00:00:52,840
Qinghe Group hasn't fallen yet.

19
00:00:53,560 --> 00:00:56,240
You're being so eager to kick us
while we're down.

20
00:00:56,440 --> 00:00:57,640
Li Ziyu.

21
00:00:57,800 --> 00:00:59,080
Why isn't she dead?

22
00:01:04,150 --> 00:01:05,040
Li Ziyu.

23
00:01:05,040 --> 00:01:06,200
Don't come any closer!

24
00:01:07,720 --> 00:01:09,460
Wasn't it supposed
to be my responsibility?

25
00:01:09,840 --> 00:01:10,680
Now what?

26
00:01:10,800 --> 00:01:12,280
No need for me to take responsibility?

27
00:01:12,280 --> 00:01:13,800
No need now.

28
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:20,080
Tell me.

29
00:01:20,520 --> 00:01:21,840
How should I take responsibility?

30
00:01:21,920 --> 00:01:22,760
Li Ziyu,

31
00:01:22,960 --> 00:01:24,120
are you a human or a ghost?

32
00:01:24,400 --> 00:01:25,280
What do you think?

33
00:01:26,680 --> 00:01:28,800
I was wrong.

34
00:01:29,240 --> 00:01:30,280
May your spirit

35
00:01:30,280 --> 00:01:31,160
rest in peace.

36
00:01:31,160 --> 00:01:32,820
Please don't come looking for me
at night.

37
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:48,120
Qinghe Group's poor internal management

38
00:01:48,680 --> 00:01:50,520
has caused losses for everyone.

39
00:01:51,850 --> 00:01:53,560
I am deeply sorry for that.

40
00:01:55,760 --> 00:01:58,240
I have the solution
to this issue in my hands.

41
00:02:02,080 --> 00:02:04,640
For those willing to help Qinghe
weather this crisis,

42
00:02:05,160 --> 00:02:06,120
from today onward,

43
00:02:06,320 --> 00:02:08,400
I will prioritize paying 10% upfront,

44
00:02:09,200 --> 00:02:11,120
with the remaining amount
paid in installments,

45
00:02:11,320 --> 00:02:13,200
and the highest interest rates applied.

46
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:15,120
How does that sound?

47
00:02:17,540 --> 00:02:19,720
After all, we won't be getting
the money anytime soon.

48
00:02:19,720 --> 00:02:21,640
Better to get something than nothing.

49
00:02:22,800 --> 00:02:24,240
Alright, I accept.

50
00:02:25,080 --> 00:02:26,240
I accept too.

51
00:02:26,800 --> 00:02:28,280
Count me in.

52
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:30,360
Well, count me in too.

53
00:02:31,280 --> 00:02:32,360
Those who accept the plan,

54
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:33,320
please follow me.

55
00:02:43,640 --> 00:02:44,640
Fine.

56
00:02:57,720 --> 00:02:58,560
What?

57
00:02:59,160 --> 00:03:01,680
You can't handle
the civilian life anymore?

58
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:04,360
Can't wait to return
and act like the fake rich lady?

59
00:03:04,600 --> 00:03:06,120
How did you know it was me?

60
00:03:06,840 --> 00:03:08,880
I thought I was well disguised.

61
00:03:09,320 --> 00:03:10,160
So,

62
00:03:10,280 --> 00:03:12,760
